WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:20.479 --> 00:00:26.309
All kinds of amazing stories happen on New Year.
Here's one of them.

00:00:27.439 --> 00:00:29.689
Red balloon

00:00:44.759 --> 00:00:52.629
One courageous balloon
flew up above the clouds
and to the Light Country.

00:00:58.779 --> 00:01:03.856
Prabu the Elephant was getting ready
for the big New Year's concert.

00:01:04.309 --> 00:01:05.039
"Flying Animals Jazz Band"

00:01:20.596 --> 00:01:23.691
Jose the Dog and Ted the Bear
were striking lightnings out of the clouds.

00:01:24.486 --> 00:01:30.236
Mustafa  the Cat caught the lightnings and made ice-cream out of them.

00:01:32.276 --> 00:01:34.576
"Ice-cream"

00:01:52.046 --> 00:01:56.131
Akira the Hare and Zoe the Cow
were wringing out thunderclouds
and turning them into fluffy white clouds.

00:01:58.436 --> 00:02:01.621
Jane the Horse colored the clouds green -
her favorite color.

00:02:33.676 --> 00:02:42.116
And this is me, Sophie.
As usual, I was working hard in the greenhouse,
growing fresh, juicy toys.

00:03:10.196 --> 00:03:15.242
Our dear Che the Turtle was baking books.

00:03:18.181 --> 00:03:19.561
"Childish Absurdity"

00:03:52.046 --> 00:03:57.976
Tembe the Fish was
looking around for lost balloons.

00:04:09.083 --> 00:04:13.473
"Lost balloon shelter"

00:04:41.276 --> 00:04:50.586
At midnight everyone gathered at
the main town square to play
the Big New Year's Concert.

00:04:55.084 --> 00:05:00.034
You will find me
I will find you

00:05:01.814 --> 00:05:07.144
By the house up
In the cloudy sky

00:05:08.936 --> 00:05:13.186
By the house up
Very-very high

00:05:15.806 --> 00:05:20.101
Far away from winters
Sad and grey

00:05:22.146 --> 00:05:28.676
So very light
So very high
